Coxisternum : Epimeral plates separated along sternal line (Fig. 15 b). Epimeral setal formula 8 - 5-6 - 5 . Epimeral setae smooth, thin, setiform, sub-equal in length ( 10–16 μm). Setae on epimeral plate I positioned on anterior, medial and posterior part of plate; those of plate II on medial part with one posterior seta (
